Simple Mandrill Email Form (jQuery)


Requires an API key from https://mandrillapp.com/
email.js line 10:        'key': 'MANDRILL_API_KEY', //Insert your unique Mandrill API Key


Either copy and paste the javascript into a JS file in your project,
or source it from your HTML and add the email.js file to your directory.

email.js lines 20-22:
  'email': '***Recipient\'s email***', //who should be recieving this email?
  'name': '***Recipient\'s name***',  //what is their name?
  'type': 'to'

replace the strings with the desired recipient.

Quick 'n easy. Enjoy
